	<h1 class="title">我的生活里男人来来往往，但真正照顾我的却是我的门卫</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75281/small/75281.jgp?1425220992" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Julie Margaret Hogben</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-01 17:57:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16862/medium/16862.jpg?1446201081" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


